    <nuclex:preferred_name>[225Ac]Ac-PSMA</nuclex:preferred_name>
    <oio:id>nuclex:000503</oio:id>
    <nuclex:definition>A therapeutic radiopharmaceutical composed of the radionuclide Actinium-225 chelated to a prostate-specific membrane antigen binding ligand.</nuclex:definition>
