    <oio:id>nuclex:000837</oio:id>
    <nuclex:definition>A sealed, ring-shaped phantom containing Germanium-68, commonly used for PET calibrations.</nuclex:definition>
    <nuclex:synonym>DQA phantom</nuclex:synonym>
