    <nuclex:preferred_name>K1 macroparameter</nuclex:preferred_name>
    <oio:id>nuclex:001217</oio:id>
    <nuclex:definition>The macroscopic rate constant describing the transport or flow of tracer from plasma to tissue, often interpreted as blood flow when the extraction is high.</nuclex:definition>
