    <oio:id>nuclex:000179</oio:id>
    <nuclex:definition>A dynamic nuclear medicine imaging procedure that continuously monitors the bladder and ureters during the phases of bladder filling and voluntary voiding to detect and quantify the retrograde flow of urine.</nuclex:definition>
